3
00:00:15,460 --> 00:00:19,240
♪Wanna try a breathless love?♪

4
00:00:19,240 --> 00:00:23,490
♪Every move hits the heart, close and sure♪

5
00:00:23,490 --> 00:00:27,460
♪Just To Meet You, you love my playful charm♪

6
00:00:27,460 --> 00:00:31,480
♪Just to meet me,
my romantic little schemes for you♪

7
00:00:31,480 --> 00:00:35,170
♪Wanna play another brand-new game?♪

8
00:00:35,170 --> 00:00:40,360
♪Layer by layer, we close the gap♪

9
00:00:40,380 --> 00:00:47,060
=Just To Meet You=

10
00:00:47,060 --> 00:00:48,700
=Episode17=
=Lang In Peril &amp; Murong Lies=

11
00:00:54,280 --> 00:00:56,390
Niannian, are you here?

12
00:00:57,670 --> 00:00:58,880
Ye Lang.

13
00:01:05,840 --> 00:01:06,790
Ye Lang.

14
00:01:07,840 --> 00:01:09,000
I'm here.

15
00:01:10,280 --> 00:01:11,120
Niannian!

16
00:01:12,280 --> 00:01:13,120
Niannian!

17
00:01:14,150 --> 00:01:14,990
Niannian!

18
00:01:15,310 --> 00:01:16,150
Niannian!

19
00:01:17,280 --> 00:01:18,120
Jiang Niannian!

20
00:01:21,310 --> 00:01:22,150
Niannian!

21
00:01:23,280 --> 00:01:24,130
Director.

22
00:01:24,150 --> 00:01:25,510
The surveillance footage

23
00:01:25,560 --> 00:01:26,400
shows no one entered.

24
00:01:28,040 --> 00:01:28,880
Keep looking.

25
00:01:30,590 --> 00:01:31,430
Niannian!

26
00:01:33,070 --> 00:01:33,910
Ye Lang.

27
00:01:39,760 --> 00:01:40,920
Are you still there?

28
00:01:45,200 --> 00:01:46,480
Are you still there?

29
00:02:06,590 --> 00:02:07,430
Niannian.

30
00:02:12,840 --> 00:02:13,680
Niannian.

31
00:02:15,000 --> 00:02:15,840
Niannian.

32
00:02:16,710 --> 00:02:17,550
Niannian.

33
00:02:19,430 --> 00:02:20,270
Niannian.

34
00:02:21,120 --> 00:02:21,960
Niannian.

35
00:02:22,710 --> 00:02:23,550
Niannian.

36
00:02:24,910 --> 00:02:25,750
Niannian.

37
00:02:31,560 --> 00:02:32,840
You came to save me.

38
00:02:33,680 --> 00:02:36,790
♪Chasing through the shadows♪

39
00:02:36,800 --> 00:02:37,640
I'm sorry.

40
00:02:38,240 --> 00:02:38,860
I'm too late.

41
00:02:41,750 --> 00:02:43,030
(This can't be an accident.)

42
00:02:43,750 --> 00:02:45,710
(Much like how her three ex-husbands died.)

43
00:02:46,840 --> 00:02:47,680
(Jiang Niannian.)

44
00:02:48,080 --> 00:02:49,590
(I won't let anything happen to you.)

45
00:03:00,870 --> 00:03:01,710
We're almost home.

46
00:03:15,000 --> 00:03:15,910
Who are you?

47
00:03:16,030 --> 00:03:16,890
Young master.

48
00:03:16,910 --> 00:03:18,680
These are medical devices
approved by Mr. Li.

49
00:03:18,780 --> 00:03:20,020
Need to be delivered here today.

50
00:03:20,910 --> 00:03:21,750
Go on, then.

51
00:03:28,120 --> 00:03:28,960
Niannian.

52
00:03:30,080 --> 00:03:31,150
Go get some rest.

53
00:03:32,190 --> 00:03:33,280
Until I'm back,

54
00:03:34,000 --> 00:03:34,840
don't open the door.

55
00:03:35,630 --> 00:03:36,470
Mm.

56
00:03:38,840 --> 00:03:39,680
Go on.

57
00:03:48,000 --> 00:03:48,840
Playing dirty, huh?

58
00:03:49,430 --> 00:03:50,400
You're tough.

59
00:03:50,870 --> 00:03:52,630
But she may not be so lucky.

60
00:03:59,520 --> 00:04:00,590
Tell your boss

61
00:04:01,240 --> 00:04:02,870
if he wants to play dirty,

62
00:04:04,280 --> 00:04:05,470
I'm in this to the end.

63
00:04:06,630 --> 00:04:08,590
But if he hurts Jiang Niannian,

64
00:04:10,560 --> 00:04:12,360
I'll make him wish they were gone.

65
00:04:13,430 --> 00:04:14,270
Get lost.

66
00:04:28,040 --> 00:04:28,880
Ye Lang.

67
00:04:29,270 --> 00:04:30,110
You okay?

68
00:05:11,600 --> 00:05:12,750
Jiang Niannian.

69
00:05:12,950 --> 00:05:13,920
Awake?

70
00:05:14,630 --> 00:05:15,660
Why is she here?

71
00:05:22,740 --> 00:05:23,580
Where's Ye Lang?

72
00:05:24,260 --> 00:05:26,260
There was an issue with an overseas deal.

73
00:05:26,620 --> 00:05:28,020
He flew to Germany at dawn.

74
00:05:29,520 --> 00:05:30,380
What?

75
00:05:30,400 --> 00:05:31,500
Something this important,

76
00:05:31,740 --> 00:05:32,700
and he didn't tell you?

77
00:05:36,090 --> 00:05:38,100
It's none of your concern.

78
00:05:44,220 --> 00:05:45,340
Then get some rest.

79
00:05:45,700 --> 00:05:46,780
Ye Lang left in a hurry,

80
00:05:47,060 --> 00:05:49,080
I've got lots of work to handle.

81
00:05:50,100 --> 00:05:50,940
After all,

82
00:05:51,140 --> 00:05:52,580
the only one who can help him now

83
00:05:53,500 --> 00:05:54,340
is me.

84
00:06:01,620 --> 00:06:02,500
By the way,

85
00:06:03,300 --> 00:06:05,260
among all those women around Ye Lang,

86
00:06:05,940 --> 00:06:07,340
you're the only one I've admired.

87
00:06:07,900 --> 00:06:09,220
Come to me if you need anything.

88
00:06:10,020 --> 00:06:10,860
I can help you.

89
00:06:20,500 --> 00:06:22,500
I wouldn't dare drink what you sent.

90
00:06:27,220 --> 00:06:28,060
That's not it.

91
00:06:28,500 --> 00:06:29,820
He wouldn't leave without a word.

92
00:06:34,100 --> 00:06:34,940
A car crash.

93
00:06:35,220 --> 00:06:36,080
Cold storage.

94
00:06:36,140 --> 00:06:36,980
A heavy object.

95
00:06:38,260 --> 00:06:39,740
That's how my three ex-husbands died.

96
00:06:43,700 --> 00:06:45,580
They're trying to kill me the same way.

97
00:06:49,180 --> 00:06:50,180
(Jiang Niannian.)

98
00:06:50,900 --> 00:06:52,420
(Didn't expect you to be so smart.)

99
00:06:53,300 --> 00:06:54,980
(You've really surprised me.)

100
00:07:02,780 --> 00:07:04,140
Luckily you were sent here in time.

101
00:07:04,460 --> 00:07:06,380
Or it would've been bad.

102
00:07:08,220 --> 00:07:09,140
Do you know

103
00:07:10,140 --> 00:07:11,100
who did it?

104
00:07:12,220 --> 00:07:13,140
Funny thing.

105
00:07:14,740 --> 00:07:16,860
Before I blacked out, I saw you there.

106
00:07:18,380 --> 00:07:19,220
What a coincidence.

107
00:07:20,100 --> 00:07:21,820
Why were you there?

108
00:07:24,060 --> 00:07:24,900
I heard

109
00:07:25,020 --> 00:07:26,220
Niannian was almost killed.

110
00:07:27,020 --> 00:07:28,700
Someone insisted on taking her home.

111
00:07:28,820 --> 00:07:29,900
I was really worried.

112
00:07:31,380 --> 00:07:32,900
Then I saw you collapse.

113
00:07:35,420 --> 00:07:36,260
Is that so?

114
00:07:44,020 --> 00:07:44,860
Where's my phone?

115
00:07:45,300 --> 00:07:46,460
It broke last night.

116
00:07:46,660 --> 00:07:47,500
Being repaired now.

117
00:07:48,020 --> 00:07:50,540
You need to rest now.

118
00:07:50,780 --> 00:07:52,140
Don't worry about anything else.

119
00:08:13,460 --> 00:08:14,740
(Could it be her?)

120
00:08:56,660 --> 00:08:57,500
Ye Lang.

121
00:08:58,180 --> 00:09:01,540
The number you have dialed is powered off.

122
00:09:01,860 --> 00:09:03,060
Why can't I get through?

123
00:09:07,460 --> 00:09:13,300
(Forensic Appraisal Report)

124
00:09:26,460 --> 00:09:27,300
Ms. Jiang.

125
00:09:27,740 --> 00:09:29,160
I've been waiting a long time.

126
00:10:19,700 --> 00:10:20,540
Are you okay?

127
00:10:23,180 --> 00:10:24,180
Why are you here?

128
00:10:25,210 --> 00:10:26,820
You should be glad I came.

129
00:10:26,820 --> 00:10:27,940
Otherwise, what would you do?

130
00:10:29,140 --> 00:10:29,980
I'm here

131
00:10:30,260 --> 00:10:31,260
to give you this.

132
00:10:43,300 --> 00:10:46,340
(Delivery Receipt)

133
00:10:59,540 --> 00:11:01,220
Based on files from Murong Xue,

134
00:11:01,220 --> 00:11:03,260
Vice President of Renxin Hospital,

135
00:11:03,740 --> 00:11:04,580
Zhang Yufeng,

136
00:11:04,660 --> 00:11:05,500
Liu Jian,

137
00:11:05,500 --> 00:11:06,420
Zhou Chen,

138
00:11:06,420 --> 00:11:07,380
my three ex-husbands,

139
00:11:07,820 --> 00:11:09,660
each had business dealings

140
00:11:09,780 --> 00:11:10,640
with the Li family

141
00:11:10,660 --> 00:11:11,940
in cold-chain, logistics

142
00:11:12,060 --> 00:11:13,220
and medical procurement.

143
00:11:13,260 --> 00:11:14,100
(Liu Yexi, God No.6)

144
00:11:14,100 --> 00:11:14,940
Through that,

145
00:11:15,100 --> 00:11:17,500
(Liu Yexi suggested Zhou Chen God No.6.)
they knew Liu Yexi.

146
00:11:18,340 --> 00:11:20,540
She recommend God No.6 to them.

147
00:11:21,140 --> 00:11:21,980
This drug claims

148
00:11:22,100 --> 00:11:23,700
to accelerate metabolism

149
00:11:23,940 --> 00:11:24,780
and slow aging.

150
00:11:25,580 --> 00:11:26,420
Gentlemen,

151
00:11:27,140 --> 00:11:28,700
you must've heard of it, right?

152
00:11:31,740 --> 00:11:33,340
It was this new drug

153
00:11:33,420 --> 00:11:34,900
that caused them three to suffer

154
00:11:34,900 --> 00:11:35,980
(Zhou Chen)
mental damage

155
00:11:35,980 --> 00:11:38,780
(Zhang Yufeng, Liu Jian)
and die in so-called accidents.

156
00:11:44,580 --> 00:11:45,460
I've looked into it.

157
00:11:46,140 --> 00:11:47,300
What Liu Yexi did

158
00:11:47,740 --> 00:11:49,700
was to corner the Li family's suppliers

159
00:11:49,900 --> 00:11:51,020
and build her own power base

160
00:11:51,340 --> 00:11:53,060
to pocket all the Li's assets.

161
00:11:53,540 --> 00:11:54,380
Gentlemen,

162
00:11:55,020 --> 00:11:55,860
you should

163
00:11:56,060 --> 00:11:57,020
watch your backs too.

164
00:12:04,260 --> 00:12:06,020
As for my three ex-husbands' cases,

165
00:12:06,380 --> 00:12:08,500
I've given all the evidence to the police.

166
00:12:08,860 --> 00:12:11,540
They will close the cases
as murder by Liu Yexi,

167
00:12:11,860 --> 00:12:13,940
to end the Li family's PR crisis.

168
00:12:14,460 --> 00:12:16,340
Once their assets are unfrozen,

169
00:12:16,420 --> 00:12:17,420
I'll use that money

170
00:12:17,660 --> 00:12:18,980
to resolve the public fallout.

171
00:12:27,340 --> 00:12:28,180
Niannian,

172
00:12:28,660 --> 00:12:29,860
you're being so thoughtful.

173
00:12:30,380 --> 00:12:31,740
I'm truly flattered.

174
00:12:32,780 --> 00:12:33,620
But,

175
00:12:34,700 --> 00:12:36,180
I really can't take your money.

176
00:12:40,020 --> 00:12:41,660
I've already signed a new contract

177
00:12:42,100 --> 00:12:43,300
with German investors.

178
00:12:44,180 --> 00:12:46,260
(Investment Agreement)
Enough to get us through this.

179
00:13:02,340 --> 00:13:03,180
Try it.

180
00:13:03,740 --> 00:13:04,600
I brought it back

181
00:13:04,620 --> 00:13:06,340
from Germany just for you.

182
00:13:06,340 --> 00:13:07,180
A Black Forest cake.

183
00:13:08,060 --> 00:13:10,540
The chef used their family cherry recipe.

184
00:13:15,460 --> 00:13:16,340
You have no idea

185
00:13:16,660 --> 00:13:17,980
how worried I've been these days

186
00:13:18,220 --> 00:13:19,020
without seeing you.

187
00:13:20,620 --> 00:13:21,460
You must be tired.

188
00:13:22,100 --> 00:13:22,940
Mm.

189
00:13:28,460 --> 00:13:29,740
Ms. Jiang,

190
00:13:31,100 --> 00:13:32,500
how should I reward you?

191
00:14:01,980 --> 00:14:03,140
We'll see

192
00:14:03,500 --> 00:14:04,340
who rewards whom.

193
00:14:24,340 --> 00:14:25,180
You're hurt?

194
00:14:26,620 --> 00:14:27,460
You lied again!

195
00:14:29,740 --> 00:14:30,980
This is your "trip abroad"?

196
00:14:33,540 --> 00:14:34,380
Niannian.

197
00:14:35,300 --> 00:14:36,140
I...

198
00:14:36,580 --> 00:14:37,420
I...

199
00:14:38,180 --> 00:14:39,580
What are you hiding from me?

200
00:14:41,020 --> 00:14:42,300
What happened?

201
00:14:44,100 --> 00:14:44,940
I just...

202
00:14:50,900 --> 00:14:51,760
Hello?

203
00:14:51,780 --> 00:14:52,620
Hello?

204
00:14:52,740 --> 00:14:54,260
Ye Lang, Xiaodi is missing.

205
00:14:56,620 --> 00:14:57,460
What did he say?

206
00:14:58,500 --> 00:14:59,340
Xiaodi...

207
00:15:00,260 --> 00:15:01,940
Niannian!

208
00:15:02,580 --> 00:15:03,460
We're on our way.

209
00:15:22,180 --> 00:15:28,740
♪Stitched-up lips
tear open a blood-red dusk♪

210
00:15:30,580 --> 00:15:36,780
♪You return reborn,
seeing through all my cracks♪

211
00:15:37,340 --> 00:15:44,340
♪This tenderness, a trap or a gift?♪

212
00:15:45,060 --> 00:15:47,540
♪Still, I'd wager my next life on it♪

213
00:15:47,540 --> 00:15:52,540
♪Just for a moment to recognize you again♪

214
00:15:52,540 --> 00:15:56,780
♪You are the blazing light in my despair♪

215
00:15:57,300 --> 00:16:01,220
♪Lighting the edges of my frozen wings♪

216
00:16:01,260 --> 00:16:05,060
♪I burn myself,
leaping into an illusion of fire♪

217
00:16:05,060 --> 00:16:10,820
♪Breaking free
from dead vines in the ashes♪

218
00:16:10,820 --> 00:16:15,140
♪You are the brightest star in the night♪

219
00:16:15,180 --> 00:16:18,980
♪Awakening my dormant fate♪

220
00:16:18,980 --> 00:16:23,500
♪Freeing me from this half-life prison♪

221
00:16:23,500 --> 00:16:28,340
♪As the bells shatter the past♪

222
00:16:28,740 --> 00:16:35,300
♪Life finds its way again♪
